21/03/2005
TIRANA, Albania -- Orthodox Archbishop Anastas Janullatos, Roman Catholic Monsignor Rrok Mirdita and Muslim leaders Hadji Selim Muca and Bectashih Hadji Reshat Bardhi signed a declaration Friday (18 March) calling for the continued promotion of religious tolerance. Prime Minister Fatos Nano was among those attending the signing ceremony. He said it sent an important message to the world. (Albanian News - 19/03/05)
